================================================================================
                            THIRD-PARTY ASSETS
================================================================================

The theme ships with placeholder WebP files at
`assets/images/sections/{squirrels,beavers,cubs,scouts,explorers,network}.webp`.
These placeholders are NOT Scout Association brand assets — they are
generic coloured circles created for testing. The theme maintainer
replaces these with the official Scout brand logos (downloaded from
https://scoutsbrand.org.uk) before publishing.

Once replaced, those files are © The Scout Association. Their distribution
within forks of this theme is permitted only if the fork is being used to
build a website for an actual Scout Group, in line with The Scout
Association's brand asset terms. Consult those terms for non-Scout-Group
use.

The colour palette presets in data/palettes.toml use hex values published in
the Scouts Brand Guidelines (Our Colours, 2023). Hex codes are factual data
and are not themselves copyrightable.

The "Inter Tight" typeface is loaded at runtime from Google Fonts under the
SIL Open Font License 1.1.
